show.description: After a painful divorce, Natasha—once a devoted housewife—reinvents herself to rise as the fearless CEO of a thriving startup. Facing betrayal, business rivalries, and personal doubts, Meera's journey from heartbreak to boardroom triumph becomes an inspiring tale of resilience and ambition.
